    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this absolute beauty. It is honestly in such incredible shape, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor yesterday! I have taken so much pride in keeping it spotless and well-loved\u2014it's basically perfect inside and out. If you're looking for a ride that looks and drives like a dream, this is the one. Come take a look, you definitely won't be disappointed!",
