    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3 in pristine condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a high-precision double VANOS variable valve timing system. The chassis is structurally flawless, with documented subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension featuring Bilstein dampers for optimized turn-in response. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers crisp engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for maximum mechanical grip. Every component, from the rod bearings to the cooling system, has been meticulously maintained to factory specifications. This is an uncompromising driver\u2019s machine with zero deferred maintenance and exceptional curb appeal.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Low mileage. Garage kept. Service records included. No mechanical issues.",
