    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector\u2019s dream, preserved in showroom condition since the day it left the dealership. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, reflecting a lifetime of professional detailing and climate-controlled storage. Inside, the cabin remains untouched by time; the premium leather seats still retain their factory scent and firm support, with every electronic component and ambient light functioning perfectly. Mechanically, it is flawless, having undergone rigorous preventative maintenance with a fully documented service history. From the pristine engine bay to the unmarked alloy wheels wrapped in fresh performance tires, every inch of this car speaks to a standard of care rarely seen on the market. This is not just a used car; it is a time capsule ready for its next discerning owner.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
