      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unrivaled caliber. This vehicle has been curated to an exacting standard, preserved in a state that mirrors its original showroom delivery. Every component, from the meticulously maintained interior to the flawless mechanical assembly, reflects a commitment to excellence. For the discerning buyer who demands nothing less than perfection, this offering represents an uncompromising opportunity to acquire a vehicle of exemplary pedigree and pristine condition.",
