    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve honestly gotta see this beauty\u2014it\u2019s like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car since day one, and it is in truly pristine condition inside and out. It drives like an absolute dream and is just waiting for a new home where it\u2019ll be just as loved. Seriously, you won't find one cleaner than this! Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 46500.0,
