    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This AP2-generation S2000 is a superlative example of Honda\u2019s high-revving engineering, featuring the F22C1 power plant with its characteristic 8,000 RPM redline and VTEC engagement. The longitudinal front-mid engine orientation ensures a perfect 50/50 weight distribution, complemented by a rigid X-bone monocoque frame and double-wishbone suspension at all four corners. This specimen remains in showroom state: the six-speed close-ratio transmission shifts with bolt-action precision, and the Torsen limited-slip differential provides optimal torque bias under load. All original VIN tags are present on factory panels, confirming a no-incident history. Mechanically stock and cosmetically flawless, this is a turnkey investment for the discerning purist.",
